The paper discusses a model of interactive unawareness, which is a concept related to game theory (cs.GT) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses different axiomatizations and approaches to unawareness, which are related to logic (cs.LO) and decision-making (cs.MA, cs.DS). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
